<title type="html"><![CDATA[10/26(Sat.) 7 Ways to Help Eliminate Knee and Joint Pain Naturally/ How To Simplify Your Life(Host:Andrew)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=328&amp;p=344#p344"><![CDATA[
Session I:<br />7 Ways to Help Eliminate Knee and Joint Pain Naturally<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://hhdresearch.org/eliminate-knee-pain-naturally/9/">http://hhdresearch.org/eliminate-knee-pain-naturally/9/</a><!-- m --><br />Q1. Why is it bad if we have knee problems?<br />Q2. Do you have knee problems? If yes, what are your symptoms? If not, how do you keep them healthy?<br />Q3. If you have knee problems which way from the article will you try? <br />Q4.Do you know any other treatment for knee pain?<br />Q5. What is your advice for someone with knee problems?<br />Session II:<br />How To Simplify Your Life<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7lECIsRif10">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7lECIsRif10</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.theschooloflife.com/thebookoflife/simplicity-anxiety/?utm_source=You%20Tube&amp;utm_medium=You%20Tube%20-%20How%20To%20Simplify%20Your%20Life%20-%20Video%20Description%20-%20TBOL%20Article&amp;utm_campaign=You%20Tube%20-%20How%20To%20Simplify%20Your%20Life%20-%20Video%20Description%20-%20TBOL%20Article">https://www.theschooloflife.com/thebook ... %20Article</a><!-- m --><br />Q1. Why do many of us long for a simpler life more than anything else?<br />Q2. What are we so stressed? Why do we feel overwhelmed by our responsibilities, schedules, commitments and obligations?<br />Q3. In order to sift through the chaotic contents of our minds, we can ask ourselves the following questions, “What is making me anxious? Who has caused me pain and how? What is exciting me?”  <br />Q4. What are some of the things we may need to do to simplify our lives? Any suggestions?<br />Q5.Would you take steps towards a simpler life or do you plan to do so in the future?  <br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=89">AndrewWang</a> — Tue Oct 22, 2019 11:27 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
